WEBVTT

00:00:00.881 --> 00:00:02.111
Imam pitanje.

00:00:03.422 --> 00:00:05.365
Može li računalo pisati poeziju?

00:00:06.959 --> 00:00:09.036
To je provokativno pitanje.

00:00:09.715 --> 00:00:11.433
Razmislite minutu

00:00:11.457 --> 00:00:14.047
i odjednom imate hrpu drugih pitanja, kao:

00:00:14.769 --> 00:00:16.150
Što je računalo?

00:00:16.710 --> 00:00:18.285
Što je poezija?

00:00:18.707 --> 00:00:20.396
Što je kreativnost?

00:00:21.650 --> 00:00:22.822
Ali to su pitanja

00:00:22.846 --> 00:00:25.916
kojima ljudi posvete
cijeli život u potrazi za odgovorom,

00:00:25.940 --> 00:00:28.164
a ne samo jedan TED Talk.

00:00:28.188 --> 00:00:30.633
Pa ćemo morati promijeniti pristup.